{"tid":335170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫學巴絲求救]  老母有個怪病  求意見","createTime":"2017-07-25T11:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T17:29:49.000Z","uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46ab1e9272ce89424a404f50db576aa54a7fcaac","tid":335170,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"老母幾個月前話訓訓下醒左<br />\n之後就覺得條頸有D 入面好似溶緊咁既感覺<br />\n佢話溶淨條條   又話覺得條頸入面有條線移位咁<br />\n冇痛症    淨係感覺唔自在   每日都keep 住有呢個感覺<br />\n訓到覺食到野      但佢本身都有情緒病    <br />\n<br />\n開頭我懷疑佢係有疑病症<br />\n但佢又話係D 感覺確實存在    日日係度量度條頸有冇溶<br />\n已經帶過佢睇過專科  照過條頸冇事,冇生瘤個D<br />\n只係有少少喉嚨發炎<br />\n<br />\n其後又帶埋佢睇精神科, 醫生就話佢有焦慮症所以咁<br />\n開左藥食過  佢話感覺冇好左,仲反而更加唔自在左<br />\n佢一直強調話<span style=\"color: red;\">條頸溶到淨番條線咁,仲要跌左落黎(好似移左位咁)</span><br />\n每日疲勞轟炸我....我都就黎比佢搞到癲<br />\n我好想了解到底佢係咩症....睇晒醫生都幫唔到佢<br />\n佢又無啦啦話咩可能係咪有污糟野搞佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇讀醫   做緊醫生既巴絲可以比D 意見我....我都好想佢好番<br />\n到底佢係真係心病定係條頸真係有D 咩線係會移位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3252ebc1e25c1dedde90712a739db2fe7da68362","tid":335170,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"連登無精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該帶佢返青山"},{"pid":"46e71ecd5059480bd5c3500e9d8806c49af3f9e7","tid":335170,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登無精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該帶佢返青山</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f00661c78be11bc173f38162605b7a99a71b1cc","tid":335170,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登無精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該帶佢返青山</blockquote><br />\n係 精神病人就大把"},{"pid":"ff12fbbc5bd7158e9a1334e73c07d9bed2cf78d1","tid":335170,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  推推"},{"pid":"92a78e58f8774944153e7297f8c85908f0f62506","tid":335170,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3dae4cb3889109693f004e6b6ad639bfafa38a","tid":335170,"uid":16338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"似思覺失調喎<br />\n幻覺其中一種"},{"pid":"ce2b430d2bb93fe03265e2059a48f3b2a30d2568","tid":335170,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似思覺失調喎<br />\n幻覺其中一種</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢又冇見到幻覺.....只係感覺唔自在"},{"pid":"1d2bff3542aaee425458d9a8afb3d60479d44815","tid":335170,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:47:41.000Z","msg":"精神病"},{"pid":"45f9583b418970bb65fbeae245a1fd166810ae99","tid":335170,"uid":13179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>似思覺失調喎<br />\n幻覺其中一種</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢又冇見到幻覺.....只係感覺唔自在</blockquote><br />\n咁精神病有好多種嘅 陪佢下次覆診精神科嘅時候如實同醫生講啦"},{"pid":"2b496ca3806f1af72d2848364417c13fa9aba26f","tid":335170,"uid":121653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"精神問題炸?"},{"pid":"556c03b27b959a455126ab19f296afbe15a8622d","tid":335170,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime